Package Services

Class ConquestMapFileReader

java.lang.Object
Services.ConquestMapFileReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ConquestMapFileReader extends Object implements Serializable
Reads a map file in Conquest format and parses it into the application's internal data structures. Supports parsing of continent, country, and neighbor data. Author: Akhilesh Kanbarkar
